OL,3,CMan avoids jail after encouraging XL
OL,4,CBully to attack police officer
OL,6,FA man has been given a suspended
OL,7,Fprison sentence for ordering an XL
OL,8,FBully to attack a police sergeant
OL,9,Fbefore trying to bite the officer
OL,10,Fhimself.
OL,12,FNathaniel Wardle, 20, was approached
OL,13,Fby police in Hexham, Northumberland on
OL,14,F31 October last year, running off with
OL,15,Fthe dogs despite being told to stop,
OL,16,FNewcastle Crown Court was told.
