OL,6,FAnother officer arrived on the scene
OL,7,Fand used PAVA spray - similar to
OL,8,Fpepper spray - and the dog was
OL,9,Fdeterred from attacking further.
OL,11,FBut Mr Pettengel said: "The defendant
OL,12,Fthen started trying to bite the
OL,13,Fofficers himself and repeatedly pulled
OL,14,Fthe dog closer to him as if trying to
OL,15,Fencourage them to attack again."
OL,17,FAfter a struggle lasting around five
OL,18,Fminutes, Wardle was arrested, claiming
OL,19,Fhe became violent because he thought
OL,20,Fthe officers were trying to seize his
OL,21,Fdogs.
