OL,6,FIn mitigation, the court was told
OL,7,FWardle had been suffering from mental
OL,8,Fhealth issues at the time of the
OL,9,Fattack after witnessing his dad being
OL,10,Funlawfully killed.
OL,12,FIan Cook, defending, said: "Life has
OL,13,Fbeen utterly chaotic for this still
OL,14,Fvery young defendant for some time.
OL,15,FThe offence involving an assault with
OL,16,Fa dog is a particularly concerning
OL,17,Foffence, deeply unpleasant.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
