OL,6,F"He has be really struggling with his
OL,7,Fmental health for some time now, since
OL,8,Fthe death of his father, who was
OL,9,Fkilled in horrific circumstances,
OL,10,Fwhich the defendant saw.
OL,12,F"Those who were alleged to have been
OL,13,Fresponsible were acquitted of his
OL,14,Ffather's murder and, for whatever
OL,15,Freason, the difficulty his father and
OL,16,Fthose people had has now been placed
OL,17,Fat the feet of the defendant and his
OL,18,Fyounger brother.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
