OL,3,CMan avoids jail after encouraging XL
OL,4,CBully to attack police officer
OL,6,F"He is continuing to have problems
OL,7,Fwith those who, in his mind, were
OL,8,Fresponsible for his father's murder."
OL,10,FJudge Stephen Earl sentenced Wardle,
OL,11,Fof Lancaster Hill, Peterlee, County
OL,12,FDurham, to two years suspended for two
OL,13,Fyears with #300 compensation.
OL,15,FThe judge told him: "You encouraged
OL,16,Fyour dog to bite him and bite him he
OL,17,Fdid and he suffered injury as a result
OL,18,Fof that."
